  <Entries>
    <Entry>
      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>[You've been climbing these impossibly steep stairs for hours, and have hours left. Your rivals know the location of the ruins, and cannot be far behind.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>2</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Use a numenera on your belt to cause a small landslide, and wipe away a segment of the stairs.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>3</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Continue towards your goal. Do not allow the terrrain to slow your progress forward.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>4</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Shake off the memory, and leave the floor unchanged.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>5</ID>
      <DefaultText>[A memory beckons you, and you comfortably step into it.  As it fills your perception, you are certain that it is linked to the mutable floor beneath your feet.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
  </Entries>
